text: Trachylepis vezo is a species of skink, a lizard in the family Scincidae. The species is endemic to Madagascar. ==References== Category:Trachylepis Category:Reptiles of Madagascar Category:Endemic fauna of Madagascar Category:Reptiles described in 1999 Category:Taxa named by Ronald Archie Nussbaum Category:Taxa named by Christopher John Raxworthy Category:Taxa named by Jean-Baptiste Ramanamanjato
title: Trachylepis vezo
